import React from 'react'
import {
  ThemeProvider,
  theme,
  ColorModeProvider,
  CSSReset,
} from '@chakra-ui/core'
import './App.css'
import { SignIn } from './pages'

const App = () => (
  <ThemeProvider theme={theme}>
    <ColorModeProvider>
      <CSSReset />
      <SignIn />
    </ColorModeProvider>
  </ThemeProvider>
)

export default App
